Class JPanelProgressGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component

            • com.qtplaf.library.swing.core.JPanelProgressGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TaskMonitor, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class JPanelProgressGroup
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements TaskMonitor
    A container for progress panels. Fills the content from left to right, up to down, with the fixed number of columns and any necessary number of rows.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
